    pred:has-phase kb:ent-phase-2 ;
    pred:has-dimension kb:ent-people ;
    pred:description "Structure organizational knowledge around the 3 Ps framework: People (who knows what — RBAC, teams, ownership, delegation, audit trails, trust scores), Policy (what governs it — legal constraints, cultural norms, compliance rules, data classification, retention policies), Procedure (how it gets done — SOPs, decision trees, process graphs, checklists, runbooks). Each dimension maps naturally to RDF triples. Key design decisions: file-based TTL delivery (portable W3C format, diffable via git, no proprietary lock-in), Bring Your Own Auth (organizations plug in existing SSO/LDAP/OIDC/SAML — no built-in identity provider), graph-native RBAC (permissions are triples, queryable and time-bounded), and self-hosted operation (n8n cloud sync on the organization's infrastructure, air-gapped first-class). Personal Reckons.AI remains unchanged; enterprise is an opt-in layer." ;
    pred:feature-id "F21" ;
    rdf:type <urn:kbase:type/Feature> ;
    pred:has-phase kb:ent-phase-4 .

